title: Why Dak Prescott Doesn't Have a Deal, Downfalls of Proposed CBA (Football 3/4)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to discuss Dak Prescott and CBA. First, the guys assess the possible deals for Dak (3:15), the hesitation from the Cowboys' side and how the impasse could eventually be resolved. Next, Will and Brady analyze the potential pitfalls of the proposed CBA and how the players could improve their side of the deal (23:30).

'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
